    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      World news story
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Information and events for British citizens in Spain
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The British Embassy and Consulates regularly hold events across Spain to update British citizens on the UK’s departure from the European Union.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
